title: Strength Cryonae
content:
Strength Cryonae is a potion made using the Alchemist profession which increases the strength of each Cryonae attack.


 * +40 Potion Strength Cryonae
 * +50 Potion Strength Cryonae
 * +60 Potent Potion Strength Cryonae
 * +70 Potion Strength Cryonae
 * +80 Potent Potion Strength Cryonae
